# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

### Dependencies ###
**/node_modules/
.pnpm-store/

### Build & Cache ###
dist/
build/
.turbo/
out/
.next/
.out/
*.tsbuildinfo
.cache/
.npm/
.flat-cache/

### Logs ###
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Runtime Data
*.timestamp-*.mjs

### Environment Variables ###
# Never commit .env files! They contain secrets.
# Provide a .env.example file instead for other developers.
.env
.env.local
.env.*
!*.env.example

### OS & Editor Specific ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.suo
*.sw?

### Test Reports ###
coverage/
.nyc_output/

### Project-Specific Ignores ###

# Secrets
apps/api/token.json
apps/api/src/scripts/antigravity.ts

# Large files, backups, and archives
*.zip
*.tar.gz
apps/api/backups/
mcp/extracted/
opencodetmp/
**/archive/

# Generated data (models, tables, etc.)
*_models_*.json
apps/api/list_tables.*
!/apps/api/list_tables.ts
latest_models/

# Ignored content
apps/api/data/agents/en/*.md
agents/*.md
debug_bashrc.txt
test.txt
